4. StatefulSet (Notes)

Database மாதிரி apps-க்கு. ஒவ்வொரு Pod-க்கும் stable name + stable storage கொடுக்கும். Pod restart ஆனாலும் same data திரும்பி கிடைக்கும்.

Deployment vs StatefulSet:

                          Deployment                        StatefulSet

Pod name                  random (my-app-7f4x2)             ordered (my-app-0, my-app-1)
Storage                   shared or none                    each pod gets own PVC
Start order               random                            ordered (0 → 1 → 2)
Use case                  stateless apps                    databases, queues

apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: StatefulSet
metadata:
  name: postgres
spec:
  serviceName: postgres
  replicas: 3
  template:
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: postgres
        image: postgres:15
        volumeMounts:
        - name: data
          mountPath: /var/lib/postgresql
  volumeClaimTemplates:             # ஒவ்வொரு pod-க்கும் தனி volume!
  - metadata:
      name: data
    spec:
      accessModes: ["ReadWriteOnce"]
      resources:
        requests:
          storage: 10Gi

Real use: MySQL, PostgreSQL, Kafka, Zookeeper, Redis Cluster.

========================================================================================================================================================

5. DaemonSet (Notes)

Cluster-ல உள்ள ஒவ்வொரு Node-லயும் automatically ஒரு Pod run ஆகும். New node join ஆனா அதுலயும் automatically start ஆகும்.

apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: DaemonSet
metadata:
  name: log-collector
spec:
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: fluentd
  template:
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: fluentd
        image: fluentd:latest
        volumeMounts:
        - name: varlog
          mountPath: /var/log      # node-ஓட logs படிக்கும்
      volumes:
      - name: varlog
        hostPath:
          path: /var/log

Real use cases:

Log collection (Fluentd, Filebeat)
Monitoring agent (Datadog, Prometheus node-exporter)
Network plugin (Calico, Cilium)
Security agent (Falco)

Cost tip: DaemonSet pods lightweight-ஆ வை — every node-ல run ஆகுறதால, heavy image = all nodes-ல memory waste.

