6. Job (Notes)

ஒரு task run பண்ணி, complete ஆனதும் pod terminate ஆகும். Server மாதிரி always-running இல்ல — run to completion.


apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: Job
metadata:
  name: db-migration
spec:
  completions: 1           # 1 successful completion வேணும்
  parallelism: 1           # ஒரே நேரத்தில் 1 pod
  backoffLimit: 3          # fail ஆனா 3 times retry
  template:
    spec:
      restartPolicy: Never
      containers:
      - name: migrate
        image: my-app:v2
        command: ["python", "manage.py", "migrate"]


kubectl get jobs                    # job status
kubectl logs job/db-migration       # output பார்க்க

Real use cases: DB migration, data processing, ML training batch, report generation, one-time scripts.

Cost tip: Job complete ஆனதும் pod automatically terminate — idle compute charge இல்ல!

