7. CronJob (Notes)

Job-ஐ schedule பண்ணி run பண்றது. Linux cron மாதிரியே — cron syntax use பண்ணும்.

apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: Cronjob
metadata:
  name: daily-report
  spec:
    schedule: "0 2 * * *"         # everyday 2 AM
    concurrencyPolicy: Forbid     # previous job running-ஆ இருந்தா, next job skip பண்ணு
    SuccessfulJobsHistoryLimit: 3   # last 3 successful jobs retain பண்ணு
    failedJobsHistoryLimit: 1       # last 1 failed job retain பண்ணு
    jobTemplate:
      spec:
        template:
          spec:
            restartPolicy: Onfailure
            containers:
            - name: reporter
              image: my-reporter:latest
              command: ["python", "generate_report.py"]


Cron syntax quick reference:

┌─ minute   (0-59)
│ ┌─ hour   (0-23)
│ │ ┌─ day  (1-31)
│ │ │ ┌─ month (1-12)
│ │ │ │ ┌─ weekday (0-6, Sun=0)
│ │ │ │ │
0 2 * * *   → every day 2AM
0 */6 * * * → every 6 hours
0 9 * * 1   → every Monday 9AM

Real use cases: Daily reports, hourly data sync, weekly cleanup, DB backup, cache warm-up.
Cost tip: CronJob-க்கு ttlSecondsAfterFinished: 300 set பண்ணு — completed job pods auto-delete ஆகும், etcd clean-ஆ இருக்கும்.

